    "body": "Currently, Spack reports curl \"errors\" when searching for binary packages in the source mirror.\r\n\r\nThese should instead fail silently, as they are expected behavior.\r\n\r\n### Rationale\r\n\r\nThe current behavior scares users and causes unnecessary bug reports.\r\n\r\nWe already have `--no-cache` and `--cache-only` options for users who are not okay with packages failing over to source.",
